description_zh: 挖掘有趣、有料的网络好内容
description_en: Discover interesting and informative online content.
submitRequirements_zh: 官方要求是免费应用，产品要求是有用或有趣。尽可能简短的介绍自己的产品
submitRequirements_en: The official requirement is for free apps, and the product requirement is to be useful or interesting.Introduce your product as briefly as possible.
rating_zh: 仅限分享和提交有创新特点的免费资源或工具，试用版或付费版不收录。
rating_en: Only free resources or tools with innovative features are allowed to be shared and submitted. Trial versions or paid versions will not be included.
